{"word":"ἐπικύρω","slug":"ἐπικύρω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐπικύρω</b></el> <el>(epic <a href='S:imperfect tense'>imperf.</a> <el>ἐπίκῡρον</el>) (epic aor1 <el>ἐπίκυρσα</el>) (or <el>ἐπικύρησα</el>) </el><p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to light upon, fall in with</i>, <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Hesiod'>Hes.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <i>to have a share, of</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}